#: ../../etc/author.rst:3
msgid "About the Author"
msgstr "關於作者"

#: ../../etc/author.rst:5
msgid ""
"Spinning Up in Deep RL was primarily developed by Josh Achiam, a research"
" scientist on the OpenAI Safety Team and PhD student at UC Berkeley "
"advised by Pieter Abbeel. Josh studies topics related to safety in deep "
"reinforcement learning, and has previously published work on `safe "
"exploration`_."
msgstr ""
"Spinning Up in Deep RL 主要由 Josh Achiam 開發，他是 OpenAI Safety Team "
"的研究科學家，同時也是 UC Berkeley 由 Pieter Abbeel 指導的博士生。Josh "
"研究與深度強化學習（deep reinforcement learning）安全性相關的主題，"
"並曾發表過關於 `safe exploration`_（安全探索）的研究。"
